snippet.textDisplay: For real and for a black man to be lynched after being doused in honey and then having a swarm of bees thrown on him by a group of white people, he sure looked like he was killing a lot of black people edit: sorry just looked it up cause I wasn’t positive on his hole origin story and he was burnt on a pyre not hung and he was already dead from bee stings, he also had his hand cut off. All that said, if their ever was a perfect movie already made that was tailored to Jordan peeles wheelhouse (if he has one) it’s Candyman, it almost could be looked at as a Jordan Peele movie from the 90s. Definitely had the racial undertones with the lynch mob killing Candyman for sleeping and impregnating a white woman and then fast forwarding and seeing the socioeconomic status of the black community in the future specifically the project that was built on top of his scattered ashes
